Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.38,0:00:07.58,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,What kind of chocolate is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.70,0:00:08.99,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,My...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.09,0:00:11.96,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,I would hope you'd know your own company's new product.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.47,0:00:16.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's that thing being sold during March for White Day...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.05,0:00:18.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The "Spy Choco White".
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.35,0:00:19.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.43,0:00:25.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a very sour white chocolate that's even\Nmore so than the popular Spy Choco Black.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.40,0:00:26.52,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.52,0:00:31.69,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Urai Taruto (53)\NUrai Confections President
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.52,0:00:29.77,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,You aren't suggesting I taste-test this stuff, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.61,0:00:33.07,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,You know I can't eat sour things, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.78,0:00:35.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haven't I always said this?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.70,0:00:37.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll handle the sweet stuff...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.07,0:00:39.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And you, the vice president, are in charge of the sour stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.91,0:00:43.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, why don't you pretend that I tricked you into taking a bite?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.16,0:00:47.33,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Urai Hoshie (49)\NUrai Taruto's Wife
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.25,0:00:47.33,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Maybe you can already withstand it, who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.63,0:00:49.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Give me a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.63,0:00:55.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wasn't it just the other day when I ate the yuzu cake you\Nmade for fun, and I ended up bedridden for a long time?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.93,0:00:57.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.43,0:01:00.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was only trying to cure your aversion to sourness.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.10,0:01:02.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Regardless...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.22,0:01:05.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have you thought of anything for the White Day speech?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.85,0:01:08.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The one on March 14th?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.86,0:01:12.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you have any ideas that would knock\Nall of those guests off their feet...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.78,0:01:16.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And instantly turn the party into a smash hit?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.45,0:01:20.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have one idea, if you'd like to try it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.41,0:01:22.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I bet everyone would be surprised!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.79,0:01:25.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Enough to make their eyes pop out?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.04,0:01:27.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,eah...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.29,0:01:30.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think even you might be surprised by this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.42,0:01:34.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Surprised to death, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.85,0:03:36.40,Signs,,0,0,0,,WHITE DAY OF BETRAYAL
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.85,0:03:36.40,Signs,,0,0,0,,(PART ONE)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.14,0:03:48.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.06,0:03:50.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was a 24-hour limit...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.06,0:03:52.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But there's less than a minute left!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.89,0:03:55.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we fail to locate the spy among the crowd by then...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.36,0:03:57.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everything will be blown to bits!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.15,0:04:02.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.70,0:04:05.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everything in a four-block radius has been cordoned off!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.45,0:04:05.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.20,0:04:07.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Youko!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.16,0:04:09.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you sure the intel is accurate!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.29,0:04:09.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.24,0:04:11.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The spy is black!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.62,0:04:12.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't make me repeat again!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.79,0:04:14.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he spy is black...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.25,0:04:15.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.21,0:04:18.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why are these chocolates all white!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.59,0:04:24.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,spyyy\NSOURRR!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.93,0:04:29.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,More sour this time â€”\hSpy Choco White!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.06,0:04:30.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Popularly on sale now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.02,0:04:33.73,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,And thanks for the support so far of Spy Choco Black!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.93,0:04:35.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran, your Dad's pretty good, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.98,0:04:37.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not to mention...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.06,0:04:40.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He even got to co-star in a commercial with his beloved Youko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.36,0:04:42.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He must've been ecstatic, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.95,0:04:47.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was complaining that no one could see much\Nof his face because of the hat and sunglasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.07,0:04:54.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it's thanks to that commercial that we were invited\Nto that sweets maker's White Day party, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.83,0:04:56.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's tonight, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.33,0:04:56.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.50,0:05:00.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It starts at 6:00 PM in Haido City Hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.25,0:05:03.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I heard that March 14th happened to be\Nthe day that company was established.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.59,0:05:07.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Speaking of White Day...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.59,0:05:09.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran, did you get one?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.05,0:05:12.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A return gift from Shinichi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.85,0:05:16.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't you give him that, Ran?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.81,0:05:18.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your handmade Valentine's chocolate!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.44,0:05:20.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rather than giving him...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.27,0:05:23.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's more like he helped himself to it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.11,0:05:29.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder if Makoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} will give me anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.07,0:05:30.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As a White Day return gift!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.95,0:05:34.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But look, not too many boys pay attention to things like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.87,0:05:38.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I doubt they would even realize that March 14th is White Day.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.33,0:05:40.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.96,0:05:44.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So if you give out chocolate on Valentine's Day...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.05,0:05:46.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll get return gifts on March 14th?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.01,0:05:48.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's music to my ears!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.14,0:05:50.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Detective Satou!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.01,0:05:52.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.10,0:05:57.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I didn't get any Valentine's chocolates from you, Satou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.23,0:06:00.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Although I waited and waited...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.23,0:06:02.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I did give you some, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.15,0:06:05.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,During the stakeout on February 14th.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.19,0:06:06.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Want one?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.28,0:06:10.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You mean that!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.20,0:06:12.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And they're like leftovers!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.99,0:06:13.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.12,0:06:15.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chocolates are like cases...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.62,0:06:17.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They are never leftovers no matter how big or small they seem!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.04,0:06:19.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.63,0:06:23.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.88,0:06:25.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Done gathering information?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.34,0:06:27.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shiratori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.18,0:06:31.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's with those boxes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.64,0:06:35.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,These are presents I'm giving Kobayashi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r} for White Day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.52,0:06:37.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.93,0:06:41.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Biscuits, candies, white chocolates, marshmallows...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.27,0:06:42.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I couldn't decide which to go with!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.98,0:06:44.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why I got them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.57,0:06:46.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, if you'll excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.15,0:06:51.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's Shiratori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.11,0:06:52.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's good at love!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.24,0:06:55.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On the other hand, look what Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} did.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.04,0:06:58.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me for not being thoughtful!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.58,0:07:04.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.09,0:07:05.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.21,0:07:08.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I forgot something!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.01,0:07:09.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please wait for me in the taxi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.97,0:07:17.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, you recovered from your cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.22,0:07:18.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You had a nasally voice didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.93,0:07:20.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm fine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.56,0:07:24.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haido City Hotel
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.27,0:07:27.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okino Youko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} couldn't make it!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.94,0:07:28.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you sure!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.36,0:07:29.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.44,0:07:33.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We were just informed that the filming for her drama went over time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.03,0:07:38.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To think I even brought a White Day present for her!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.45,0:07:39.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.91,0:07:42.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You haven't even given anything to Mom or me yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.83,0:07:45.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, great detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.71,0:07:49.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Welcome to Urai Confection's 8th anniversary party!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.60,0:07:51.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uhm...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.55,0:07:53.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You are...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.43,0:07:57.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I am president of Urai CÃ¶nfections, Urai Taruto.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.68,0:07:59.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I believe this is our first meeting, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.85,0:08:01.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,President!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.06,0:08:02.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.98,0:08:05.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is my wife and vice president...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.69,0:08:06.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm Hoshie.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.06,0:08:08.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's an honor to meet you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.07,0:08:10.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sleeping Kogorou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sama{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.24,0:08:12.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.74,0:08:13.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm really flattered!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.41,0:08:22.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is truly magnificent!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.79,0:08:23.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.42,0:08:26.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look at all the people here, Conan kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.42,0:08:29.25,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Here, here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.88,0:08:31.71,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,It's served in a buffet style.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.71,0:08:35.26,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Please help yourselves to whatever food or drinks you'd like!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.56,0:08:43.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Take a look here, Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.06,0:08:44.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a grand selection!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.77,0:08:46.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You guys better hurry and pick!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.10,0:08:47.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fried prawns, fried prawns!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.77,0:08:48.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.44,0:08:51.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uncle, you're too greedy...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.28,0:08:55.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.45,0:08:58.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As expected of Haido City Hotel, their cuisine is first-class!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.82,0:09:00.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, what do you think he'll show us?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.66,0:09:02.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.83,0:09:04.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,President Urai!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.71,0:09:09.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,According to Sonoko, he always does\Nsomething interesting at every party.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.04,0:09:11.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Doing things like magic tricks...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.46,0:09:14.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dressing in a costume used in the commercials...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.22,0:09:17.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or even doing a short skit under the spotlight, she said!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.26,0:09:21.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I wonder if everyone's expecting,something this time as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.68,0:09:25.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A skit, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.19,0:09:31.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, you delivered a fine performance in the commercial.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.40,0:09:32.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Absolutely!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.57,0:09:35.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were the right man for the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.40,0:09:36.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nah, nah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.49,0:09:45.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually, it was Youko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} who reguested you to us by saying,\NGive Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} the role of my investigative partner by all means."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.29,0:09:47.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's because...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.71,0:09:50.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's enamored with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.08,0:09:51.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not it...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.88,0:09:52.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.84,0:09:55.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And now, for one of the leading actors of the commercial...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.13,0:09:59.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please welcome the great detective Mouri Kogorou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sama{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.64,0:10:06.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.81,0:10:10.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh yes, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.02,0:10:10.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.98,0:10:12.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would you like me to read your palm?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.15,0:10:14.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Read... my palm?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.86,0:10:18.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't know you were well-versed in palm reading.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.41,0:10:23.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I always read yours before waking you up each morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.41,0:10:28.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You have a short lifeline, so be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.37,0:10:30.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't want to have a nearly death.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.25,0:10:31.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.75,0:10:34.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now since our topic is Sour Spy Choco...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.63,0:10:37.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I, Mouri Kogorou, will share some of my investigation\Nstories where I made some...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.63,0:10:39.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Very sour!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.13,0:10:42.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, very sorry mistakes, with all of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.68,0:10:46.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}, your luck is strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.97,0:10:51.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your intuition line is extending from your luna\Nmount towards the base of your little finger.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.94,0:10:53.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I do often win prize drawings!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.94,0:10:57.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uhm...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.82,0:11:00.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How's my luck with love?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.78,0:11:04.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.62,0:11:08.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your marriage line runs sideways and is Y-shaped.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.70,0:11:12.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This means you haven't been able to bond with the\Nperson you like because of numerous obstacles...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.83,0:11:15.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And it appears that you're headed towards despair.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.00,0:11:17.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.46,0:11:19.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,chanto kiiteru\NAre you still listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.59,0:11:21.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.72,0:11:22.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm listening!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.55,0:11:24.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I meant you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.26,0:11:27.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perhaps.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.77,0:11:34.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But there's a good chance that you'll finally\Nbe together at the end of a dramatic event.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.44,0:11:36.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So try not to quarrel with him too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.69,0:11:38.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.08,0:11:52.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.21,0:11:53.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What now, dear?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.79,0:11:57.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you doing a mystery skit this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.13,0:12:03.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Detective Mouri?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.55,0:12:04.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.05,0:12:07.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It appears to be your turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.01,0:12:08.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.56,0:12:11.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.27,0:12:13.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He should've told me about this beforehand!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.27,0:12:16.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh my, look at this man.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.06,0:12:18.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He really looks like he's dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.07,0:12:22.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.82,0:12:25.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The estimated time of death is 19:54 hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.45,0:12:29.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If my intuition as a long-time detective is correct...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.79,0:12:32.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit is, without a doubt...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.75,0:12:34.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right in this room!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.58,0:12:37.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.67,0:12:39.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do I do next?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.13,0:12:41.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,President Urai!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.01,0:12:42.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.26,0:12:44.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.68,0:12:46.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He can't answer you no matter how much you try.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.14,0:12:49.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because this person...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.05,0:12:49.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't breathing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.93,0:12:53.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's dead!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.14,0:12:53.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.85,0:12:55.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.73,0:12:57.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is a joke, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.31,0:12:57.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dear?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.61,0:12:59.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dear!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.15,0:13:01.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dear!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.49,0:13:04.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The scent of almond is emanating from his mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.40,0:13:06.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That of cyanide derivatives...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.82,0:13:10.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Death by poison.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.71,0:13:19.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The deceased is Urai Toruto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, 53 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.09,0:13:21.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was the president of Urai Confections...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.59,0:13:23.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the host of this party.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.17,0:13:27.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I heard from the coroner that it was death by poison.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.76,0:13:28.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.59,0:13:31.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They said it was acute medicinal poisoning\Nvia a hydrocyanic acid compound.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.43,0:13:35.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, the ones who were by the president's\Nside when he collapsed were...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.89,0:13:37.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.90,0:13:41.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The president's wife, who is the vice president of Urai Confections...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.86,0:13:45.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Urai Hoshie{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} â€”\honly these three people?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.28,0:13:46.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.20,0:13:47.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.03,0:13:52.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I believe it was right as Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was giving a speech on stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.79,0:13:57.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My husband let out a groan all of a sudden and collapsed...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.62,0:13:59.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And he hasn't moved since.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.75,0:14:05.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I recall, the person right next to the president was you, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.30,0:14:05.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.72,0:14:08.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was reading Ranchan's palm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.26,0:14:10.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Her palm?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.47,0:14:11.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.30,0:14:12.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.43,0:14:17.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She was holding my left hand with both of her hands to read it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.14,0:14:21.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If both of her hands were occupied...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.61,0:14:24.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She couldn't have manually administered the poison.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.86,0:14:30.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At that time, did the wife tell the president to do anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.61,0:14:33.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like tell him to eat or drink something?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.33,0:14:34.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.33,0:14:36.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.25,0:14:39.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She did say this while in the middle of reading\NRan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}'s palm, didn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.50,0:14:42.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you still listening?"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.17,0:14:45.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.38,0:14:49.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At first I thought she was talking to me, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.68,0:14:52.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It turned out she was actually asking the president.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.43,0:14:56.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because it's a rare opportunity to hear Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s\Nspeech, yet his mind seemed absent.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.89,0:15:02.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the president's reply at the time was kind of strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.44,0:15:04.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.57,0:15:07.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He didn't reply with "l'm listening" or "I wasn't listening"...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.15,0:15:11.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But instead, he said, "Ah, perhaps".
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.82,0:15:14.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That is indeed strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.53,0:15:18.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As an answer to whether he was still listening to my speech or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.20,0:15:23.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I suppose my husband gave such an ambiguous\Nanswer because he was quite distracted.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.75,0:15:26.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not to mention that, after Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s speech...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.05,0:15:29.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was planning to make an important announcement.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.09,0:15:30.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Important announcement?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.88,0:15:31.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.38,0:15:35.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That we were to be divorced and split the company into two.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.81,0:15:37.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.68,0:15:38.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is it true?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.97,0:15:39.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.14,0:15:43.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Urai Confections had gotten large enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.19,0:15:46.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And we've often bumped heads due to differences\Nof opinion in management styles.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.78,0:15:52.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Although he did cry and beg me to reconsider.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.07,0:15:56.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Saying, "I don't mind splitting the company,\Nbut please don't divorce me."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.95,0:15:59.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Without you, I can't go on."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.83,0:16:01.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that case, could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.12,0:16:04.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Broken up over this, he committed suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.42,0:16:05.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems to be a viable possibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.42,0:16:09.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that were the case, it would be a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.71,0:16:12.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm a pro at sour products as he was with sweets.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.68,0:16:18.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought I had convinced him to do what we do\Nbest and to take our expertises to the limit...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.14,0:16:21.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, my friend was saying...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.31,0:16:25.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That both the president and you were\Nconfectionery contest champions.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.31,0:16:27.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.40,0:16:28.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Only my husband was.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.78,0:16:33.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I took second, and didn't win the championship.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.75,0:16:35.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.70,0:16:36.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.53,0:16:37.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In any event...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.53,0:16:40.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you're going to conduct a body search\Non me, could you please hurry up?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.96,0:16:45.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If there were a culprit who administered poison to my husband...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.79,0:16:48.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It couldn't be anyone other than me who was next to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.34,0:16:54.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that's the case, it's possible that I still have evidence\Nthat I had the poison in my possession, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.59,0:16:56.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.55,0:17:02.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,However, it'd be a big help if you used the staff\Nroom past the door in the back to search me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.64,0:17:09.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since I'm sure the media is at the front door, trying\Nto rush in and get details about this incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.23,0:17:13.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I were escorted out there by an officer...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.90,0:17:17.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They'd take it to mean that I was being\Napprehended and taken to the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.95,0:17:19.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good point...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.53,0:17:20.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, Satou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.78,0:17:21.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.66,0:17:22.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.91,0:17:23.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.08,0:17:25.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.41,0:17:26.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let us through please.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.38,0:17:34.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.59,0:17:39.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I shouldn't have worn such high heels to the party...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.60,0:17:41.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you need a shoulder to lean on?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.22,0:17:43.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.85,0:17:45.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's only a small sprain.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.60,0:17:48.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's get this over with quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.28,0:17:56.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector Megure...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.86,0:17:59.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll take these with us to examine them further, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.95,0:18:05.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems that none of the food or drink on\Nthis table have had any poison applied.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.41,0:18:06.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.89,0:18:07.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.92,0:18:11.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Although the wife had some lemon\Ntea, I don't think he drank any of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.59,0:18:16.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After all, the president's aversion to sourness was well known.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.17,0:18:17.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.97,0:18:22.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.01,0:18:23.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.47,0:18:28.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I haven't eaten anything since breakfast...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.98,0:18:32.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And just when I was about to eat dinner, I was called here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.07,0:18:37.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But doesn't your wife always make you a boxed lunch with love?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.90,0:18:38.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.07,0:18:42.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Midori and I had a Iittle fight before I left home to work...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.41,0:18:47.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm asking you, isn't there something you want to give me today!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.12,0:18:48.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What on earth do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.37,0:18:53.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It really doesn't matter, so don't ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.30,0:19:02.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those are souvenir gift bags for this White Day party.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.68,0:19:04.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you'd like how about taking one home?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.68,0:19:06.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.10,0:19:08.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"White Day"?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.27,0:19:09.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.73,0:19:15.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the judgment day when the extent of your boyfriend's\Nlove will be exposed in broad daylight!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.86,0:19:18.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,First, you casually give him chocolate on Valentine's Day.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.90,0:19:22.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And if he returns the favor exactly one month later on March 14th...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.57,0:19:25.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The jolly bells of blinding romance will resound!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.37,0:19:28.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he doesn't, the footsteps of catastrophe will close in.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.91,0:19:31.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Footsteps of catastrophe!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.58,0:19:34.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me for not being thoughtful!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.00,0:19:37.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.55,0:19:40.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you done with that heel?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.09,0:19:41.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.84,0:19:43.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, the other one...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.60,0:19:45.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not now, not now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.68,0:19:47.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Focus on work, focus!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.60,0:19:49.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.02,0:19:51.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A run-up murder?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.81,0:19:52.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.64,0:19:54.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's correct, Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.23,0:20:01.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From what I've heard, each year the'president puts on\Na performance at this party to surprise the guests.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.95,0:20:07.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Showing magic, dressing in costumes, or doing skits.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.99,0:20:08.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In short...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.87,0:20:12.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When the president first yelled out and collapsed,\Nit was an act as part of the skit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.42,0:20:19.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perhaps he was planning to rope me, the great detective Mouri\NKogorou and a special guest, into doing a mystery skit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.50,0:20:22.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not knowing that he'd actually be killed soon afterwards!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.47,0:20:26.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, the first person who ran up to the fallen president was...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.55,0:20:28.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.56,0:20:32.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She knelt down next to the president's face and said this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.10,0:20:34.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, what now, dear?"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.94,0:20:37.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Are you doing a mystery skit this time?"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.02,0:20:39.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could she have administered the poison...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.98,0:20:42.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Directly into his mouth at that time!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.95,0:20:43.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.70,0:20:46.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words, this crime was impossible\Nfor anyone except his wife...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.74,0:20:48.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who knew the content of the skit!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.95,0:20:49.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.29,0:20:53.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To think that a great detective would utter such nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.17,0:20:58.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At the time you were on stage and may not have seen it, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.34,0:21:04.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After my husband collapsed, he didn't twitch even\Nonce and we didn't hear him make a sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.51,0:21:09.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I had really given him the poison at that time...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.35,0:21:13.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He would've struggled painfully and let out a groan, wouldn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.89,0:21:15.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.19,0:21:15.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.31,0:21:17.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were next to them, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.77,0:21:20.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's just like she said...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.40,0:21:23.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He didn't move at all and really seemed like he was dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.19,0:21:25.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.45,0:21:28.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your deduction just now was the one you\Noften blurt out before you get serious...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.41,0:21:32.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Namely the absurd and fatuous " fail version", am I correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.37,0:21:34.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fail version?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.62,0:21:37.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Although this is the one I remember best...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.42,0:21:47.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, where'd the cigarette butt fly off to!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.22,0:21:48.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.01,0:21:49.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The results of the body search?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.59,0:21:50.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.43,0:21:54.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I found no traces of poison nor any traces\Nthat she had handled posion.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.81,0:21:56.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And that's only natural.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.56,0:21:58.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that case, this was indeed...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.23,0:21:59.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.98,0:22:03.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the glove compartment of the president's car...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.19,0:22:06.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We found bottled poison and a case filled with medicinal wafers.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.03,0:22:08.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By wafers, you mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.78,0:22:12.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The thingamajig you enclose powdered medicine\Nin that soon dissolves in your mouth?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.03,0:22:13.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.04,0:22:14.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I mentioned that to the coroner...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.91,0:22:18.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They said that they'd found a half-dissolved\Nwafer between the president's rear teeth.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.37,0:22:20.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.42,0:22:23.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He hid the wafer containing the poison in his pocket...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.63,0:22:25.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And chose the right moment to take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.76,0:22:27.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This does appear to be a suicide after all, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.43,0:22:34.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit is definitely the wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.43,0:22:37.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, just how did she do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.87,0:24:06.03,Signs,,0,0,0,,NEXT EPISODE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.89,0:24:01.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The tragedy that befalls on White Day...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.77,0:24:05.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's the miracle trick hidden in the sour\Nlemon that turns the impossible possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.61,0:24:09.30,Signs,,0,0,0,,WHITE DAY OF BETRAYAL
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.61,0:24:09.30,Signs,,0,0,0,,(PART TWO)
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.74,0:24:17.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Detective Conan was brought to you by these sponsors.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.90,0:24:29.00,Signs,,0,0,0,,Lemon
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.60,0:24:26.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan's Hint
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.30,0:24:34.76,Signs,,0,0,0,,LOOK FORWARD TO THE NEXT EPISODE
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.61,0:24:31.61,Signs,,0,0,0,,Inspector, the more\Nyou squeeze the\Nlemon, the more\Nsour it gets!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.70,0:24:34.76,Signs,,0,0,0,,Idiot! Why don't\Nyou squeeze your\Nbrain instead!?
